Shifu受行业领导者信任.message: Shifu is trusted by industry leaders

让开发产业场景像开发APP一样简单！.message: Make developing industrial scenes as easy as developing an app!

大到使用私有驱动的工程机械.message: Large to construction machinery using private driver

小到使用公有协议的温湿度计.message: Small to thermometers using public protocol

Shifu超高兼容性让你轻松应对各种易购设备.message: Shifu's high compatibility allows you to easily handle a variety of e-bay devices

所有接入Shifu的设备及应用都会被封装成一个拼图式模块.message: All devices and applications connected to Shifu are packaged into a puzzle-like module

根据场景内的设备不同，按需加载即可.message: Just load as needed, depending on the devices in the scene

接入设备后，Shifu会自动把设备的能力抽象成API.message: After accessing the device, Shifu will automatically abstract the device's capabilities into an API

让你的应用和硬件设备彻底解耦.message: Completely decouple your application from the hardware device

把低效的物联网应用开发变得像面向对象编程一样高效.message: Make inefficient IoT application development as efficient as object-oriented programming

Shifu已通过在航天场景验证.message: Shifu has been validated in aerospace scenarios

让你远离宕机烦恼.message: Keeps you out of downtime trouble

联合国的云原生安全团队操刀.message: The UN's cloud-native security team is at the helm

无论是数据加密还是网络安全.message: Whether it is data encryption or network security

Shifu得益于Kubernetes原生架构.message: Shifu benefits from Kubernetes native architecture

可以无缝接入强大的云原生软件生态.message: And seamlessly accesses to a powerful cloud-native software ecosystem

让全球的开发者帮你解决后顾之忧.message: Let the world's developers help you with your worries

无论是协议规定的数据，还是驱动返回值，Shifu都能自动采集。.message: Whether the data is specified by the protocol or returned by the driver, Shifu is able to record it automatically.

Shifu的核心代码全部开源，让您避免供应商锁定。您更可以自由地选择让Shifu.message: Shifu's core codes are all open source, allowing you to avoid vendor lock-in. You are even free to choose to have Shifu deployed on-premises, on edge, private, hybrid or public clouds.

k8s已经一统天下，Shifu基于k8s的架构可以让你免去未来迁移到k8s上的烦.message: k8s has ruled the roost, and Shifu's k8s-based architecture can save you the trouble of migrating to k8s in the future.

只需一个2G内存的树莓派就可以在生产环境跑起Shifu。.message: Just a Raspberry Pi with 2G RAM can run Shifu in a production environment.

Shifu兼容所有基于k8s的云边协同框架（OpenYurt, KubeEdge.message: Shifu is compatible with all k8s-based cloud edge collaboration frameworks (OpenYurt, KubeEdge, etc.).

基于k8s的架构让Shifu可以无限扩容，轻松处理亿级设备接入，连智慧城市项目都.message: The k8s-based architecture allows Shifu to scale infinitely and easily handle billions of device access, even for smart city projects.
